    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint remains vibrant and holds a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chipping on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful regular use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with only minimal curb rash on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the upholstery is free of rips or stains, though the driver\u2019s seat shows typical entry-wear on the bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It features a complete service log, including a recently replaced battery and a full fluid flush performed last season. The tires provide excellent grip with plenty of life left, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This car drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a comfortable, quiet ride. It is a solid, honest vehicle that is ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required.",
